OL,3,CFormer Football League manager Kenny
OL,4,CJackett dies, aged 64
OL,6,FFormer Wolves manager Kenny Jackett
OL,7,Fhas died, aged 64.
OL,9,FHe was in charge at Molineux for three
OL,10,Fseasons, joining in the summer of 2013
OL,11,Fafter Wolves suffered back-to-back
OL,12,Frelegations, dropping from the Premier
OL,13,FLeague to League One.
OL,15,FIn his first season, Jackett earned
OL,16,Fpromotion, guiding Wolves back to the
OL,17,FChampionship with 103 points, at the
OL,18,Ftime a record for League One.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
