PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781266277
OL,3,CFormer Football League manager Kenny
OL,4,CJackett dies, aged 64
OL,6,FThis record lasted 11 years, broken by
OL,7,FBirmingham City, who recorded 111
OL,8,Fpoints in the 2024/25 season.
OL,10,FIn Wolves' first season back in the
OL,11,FChampionship, they narrowly missed out
OL,12,Fof the play-off places.
OL,14,FHe left Wolves in July 2016 after the
OL,15,Fclub was purchased by Chinese
OL,16,Fconglomerate Fosun International.
OL,18,FThe club posted on their X (formerly
OL,19,FTwitter) account today, paying tribute
OL,20,Fto their former manager.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
