OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781266277
OL,3,CFormer Football League manager Kenny
OL,4,CJackett dies, aged 64
OL,6,F"Wolves are devastated to learn of the
OL,7,Fpassing of our former manager Kenny
OL,8,FJackett.
OL,10,F"Kenny led the club to its incredible
OL,11,Frecord-breaking League One title and
OL,12,Flaid the foundations for the club as
OL,13,Fwe know it today.
OL,15,F"The thoughts of everyone at Wolves
OL,16,Fare with Kenny's family and friends at
OL,17,Fthis time."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
