PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781266277
OL,3,CFormer Football League manager Kenny
OL,4,CJackett dies, aged 64
OL,6,FJackett also had spells in charge of
OL,7,FWatford, Millwall, Swansea City,
OL,8,FRotherham, Portsmouth and Leyton
OL,9,FOrient during a lengthy managerial
OL,10,Fcareer.
OL,12,FAs a player, he made 428 appearances
OL,13,Ffor Watford and earned 31 caps for
OL,14,FWales.
OL,16,FHis final role in the game was as
OL,17,Fdirector of football at Gillingham
OL,18,Fbefore he stepped down for medical
OL,19,Freasons in November 2024.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
